X,Y\subseteq \mathbb{R}^n
\begin{align*} X+Y &= \{\mathbf{x}+\mathbf{y}\mid \mathbf{x}\in X,\mathbf{y}\in Y\}\\ &= \bigcup_{\mathbf{y}\in Y} (X+\mathbf{y})\\ &=\bigcup_{\mathbf{x}\in X} (Y+\mathbf{x}). \end{align*}
